{"tid":1119303,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"自動熄機再自動開機 點搞","createTime":"2019-04-21T21:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T04:59:43.000Z","uid":86750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a285ac25613a95b07c54a8708574f6b9a530866f","tid":1119303,"uid":86750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T21:34:13.000Z","msg":"情況就係用用下無端端成部機熄左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n耳機啪咗聲<br />\n之後識自己開返機<br />\n但係入到os 就算無用 過一陣都係會再自己熄機 係咁loop<br />\n不過無論係普通開機定重開機都好似要boot一陣先真係著<br />\n<br />\n有清下塵 有較大風扇 有拆RAM出嚟擦下 有拆哂機殻power switch d線就咁短路開機 都無用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前幾日開始會無端端上網斷線 但手機wifi上到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一諗到係底板 第二火牛 仲有無其他可能性 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44cc6569da1935a56d65483e9785f5d38913cd8a","tid":1119303,"uid":86750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T21:40:34.000Z","msg":"唔記得咗spec <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIntel i5 6500<br />\nMSI GTX 750 Ti Dual Fan<br />\nMSI B150M Gaming Pro<br />\nKingston 8GB Ram<br />\nANTEC TruePower Classic 550W"},{"pid":"f7c9c9dfba8be1a14d7af36468c7aff72e2b873a","tid":1119303,"uid":194743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T21:44:07.000Z","msg":"cpu 過熱 睇左溫度未"},{"pid":"fc997d05df1e0aa86cd688ab24b7a46640c6e100","tid":1119303,"uid":194743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T21:44:36.000Z","msg":"如果唔係  就係底版問題"},{"pid":"1f2f2e6179217a4f24531ca4e902cd5707e77991","tid":1119303,"uid":194743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T21:45:21.000Z","msg":"重有可能就係中毒"},{"pid":"eada53c81fa6d48de54ec5730c047e7474279731","tid":1119303,"uid":194743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T21:45:59.000Z","msg":"睇溫度先 如唔得重裝window 再唔得換底版